        "author_role": "OWNER",
        "timestamp": "2021-06-03 13:18:27.000000000",
        "message": "Patch Set 1:\n\n> Patch Set 1: Code-Review+1\n> \n> Is Policy Audit in the TOSCA Spec?\n\nThe audit is to register when policy deploy/undeploy is requested from PAP. the Tosca Identifier is referred (name/version). Let me know if this is enough to answer your question or if you need further info.",
        "patchset_number": 1
